      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with no major issues, providing a reliable driving experience for its next owner. While the interior and exterior show some minor signs of regular use and age, there are no significant defects or damage to report. It is a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
