    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in superlative condition, this vehicle exemplifies the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every facet, from its pristine exterior finish to the meticulously maintained cabin, remains in showroom state. This is an uncompromising opportunity for the collector or enthusiast who demands excellence without exception. We invite you to experience a standard of quality that transcends the ordinary.",
