    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade example that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its deep, glass-like factory finish with zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state\u2014the premium leather bolsters show no signs of compression, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; a comprehensive binder containing every service receipt since new is included, documenting proactive maintenance far beyond manufacturer recommendations. From the pristine undercarriage to the matching set of high-performance tires with near-full tread, every inch of this car has been scrutinized. This is not just a well-kept car; it is a time-capsule investment for the most discerning collector who demands absolute perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
